---
// Kontakt.astro - Wersja Light Premium: Czystość i Konwersja
---
<section id="kontakt" class="py-24 bg-white relative overflow-hidden border-t border-slate-100">
  
  <div class="sr-only">
    <h2>Kontakt – Ekspert Power BI i Excel Katowice</h2>
    <p>
      Szukasz specjalisty od danych na Śląsku? Skontaktuj się z Raporty24. Oferujemy 
      <strong>usługi Excel</strong>, wdrażanie <strong>dashboardów Power BI</strong> oraz 
      <strong>automatyzację procesów</strong> dla firm. Zapytaj o darmowy <strong>audyt danych</strong> 
      i optymalizację Twoich raportów.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    
    <header class="max-w-4xl mb-20">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20">
        <span class="flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 shadow-[0_0_10px_#22c55e]"></span>
        <span class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-green-700">Get in touch</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter text-slate-900 mb-8 leading-[0.95]">
        Gotowy na <br/><span class="text-green-600 italic">automatyzację?</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        Przestań marnować czas na ręczną pracę z danymi. Napisz do nas i dowiedz się, jak <strong class="text-slate-900">ekspert Power BI</strong> może przyspieszyć Twój biznes.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-start">
      
      <div class="space-y-12">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-8 uppercase tracking-tight">Bezpośrednia ścieżka</h3>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <a href="mailto:biuro@raporty24.pl" class="group flex items-center gap-6 text-xl text-slate-600 hover:text-green-600 transition-all">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-[1.5rem] flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm group-hover:bg-green-600 group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-500">
                <i class="fas fa-envelope text-xl"></i>
              </div>
              <span class="font-bold border-b-2 border-slate-100 group-hover:border-green-600 pb-1 transition-all">biuro@raporty24.pl</span>
            </a>
            
            <a href="tel:+48784391076" class="group flex items-center gap-6 text-xl text-slate-600 hover:text-green-600 transition-all">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-[1.5rem] flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm group-hover:bg-green-600 group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-500">
                <i class="fas fa-phone text-xl"></i>
              </div>
              <span class="font-bold border-b-2 border-slate-100 group-hover:border-green-600 pb-1 transition-all">+48 784 391 076</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-10 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-[2.5rem] group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-32 h-32 bg-green-500/5 rounded-full blur-2xl transition-all"></div>
          <h4 class="font-black text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt text-green-600"></i> Twoje dane są bezpieczne
          </h4>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Szanujemy Twoją prywatność. Jako <strong>specjaliści Excel i Power BI</strong>, dbamy o najwyższe standardy poufności. Twoje dane służą wyłącznie do przygotowania darmowej wyceny.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-[2.5rem] p-10 lg:p-12 shadow-2xl shadow-slate-200/50 relative">
        <form
          name="kontakt"
          method="POST"
          data-netlify="true"
          action="/thanks"
          netlify-honeypot="bot-field"
          class="space-y-8"
        >
          <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="kontakt" />
          <p class="hidden"><label>Bot field: <input name="bot-field" /></label></p>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <label class="text-[10px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest ml-1">Imię i nazwisko*</label>
              <input
                type="text"
                name="name"
                required
                placeholder="Jan Kowalski"
                class="w-full px-6 py-4 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 text-slate-900 placeholder:text-slate-300 focus:border-green-500 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-green-500/5 outline-none transition-all"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <label class="text-[10px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest ml-1">Email*</label>
              <input
                type="email"
                name="email"
                required
                placeholder="jan@firma.pl"
                class="w-full px-6 py-4 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 text-slate-900 placeholder:text-slate-300 focus:border-green-500 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-green-500/5 outline-none transition-all"
              />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-3">
            <label class="text-[10px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest ml-1">Cel rozmowy*</label>
            <div class="relative">
              <select
                name="temat"
                required
                class="w-full px-6 py-4 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 text-slate-900 appearance-none focus:border-green-500 outline-none transition-all cursor-pointer"
              >
                <option value="" disabled selected>Wybierz cel rozmowy</option>
                <option value="wycena">Wycena usługi / Projekt BI</option>
                <option value="abonament">Abonament / Stałe wsparcie</option>
                <option value="szkolenie">Szkolenia Power BI / Excel</option>
                <option value="inne">Inne zapytanie</option>
              </select>
              <div class="absolute right-6 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none text-slate-400">
                <i class="fas fa-chevron-down text-xs"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-3">
            <label class="text-[10px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest ml-1">Twoje wyzwanie*</label>
            <textarea
              name="wiadomosc"
              required
              rows="4"
              placeholder="Opisz krótko swój problem lub proces, który chcesz zautomatyzować..."
              class="w-full px-6 py-4 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 text-slate-900 placeholder:text-slate-300 focus:border-green-500 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-green-500/5 outline-none transition-all resize-none"
            ></textarea>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="w-full py-5 bg-green-600 rounded-2xl text-white font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] shadow-xl shadow-green-600/20 hover:bg-green-700 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
            Wyślij zgłoszenie
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="absolute -bottom-1/4 -left-1/4 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-green-500/[0.03] rounded-full blur-[120px] -z-10"></div>
</section>